      <title>市场条件有利于撤资，意大利加大 Paschi 销售力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/italy-steps-up-paschi-sale-as-market-conditions-favor-divestment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利正在采取行动，遵守欧盟的要求，处置锡耶纳银行 (Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA)，利用有利的市场条件和该银行在扭亏为盈方面取得的进展，因为竞争对手缺乏兴趣，导致合并的可能性较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/italy-steps-up-paschi-sale-as-market-conditions-favor-divestment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
